    "note": "Fail-closed enumeration from the phase-1 sweep: convert_m5.py rebuilds this inventory from the converted JSON (build/report/m5_text_inventory.json) and exits nonzero if any BINARY assert_invalid/assert_malformed text, trap/exhaustion/uninstantiable text, action type, or command type outside these sets appears - a new judgment surface must be enumerated here first, never absorbed silently. TEXT-format assert_malformed/assert_invalid texts are not constrained: those commands are UNSUPPORTED (no .wat parser at this milestone) and their texts are inventory-only."
